There 2 different types of food: apricot, kiwi
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the doctor is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Food         | apricot          | kiwi     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 